KEEP FROZEN UNTIL READY TO BAKE
Remove frozen pizza from package. For food safety and quality, the pizza must
be cooked until the centre of the pizza reaches an internal temperature of
167'F (75 C), and the cheese is completely melted and the crust is goiden brown.
